<h3 id="ada-224_3">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]224.3 Beds[-END TRANSLATE-]</h3>
<p class="standards">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]In guest rooms having more than 25 beds, 5 percent minimum of the beds shall have clear floor space complying with[-END TRANSLATE-] <a href="#ada-806_2_3" class="navSectionLink">806.2.3</a>.</p>
<h3 id="ada-224_4">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]224.4 Guest Rooms with Communication Features[-END TRANSLATE-]</h3>
<p class="standards">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]In transient lodging facilities, guest rooms with communication features complying with[-END TRANSLATE-] <a href="#ada-806_3" class="navSectionLink">806.3</a> [-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]shall be provided in accordance with Table 224.4.[-END TRANSLATE-]</p>
