<h5 id="ada-703_7_2_2">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]703.7.2.2 International Symbol of TTY[-END TRANSLATE-]</h5>
<p class="standards">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]The International Symbol of TTY shall comply with Figure 703.7.2.2.[-END TRANSLATE-]</p>
