<h5 id="ada-703_7_2_4">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]703.7.2.4 Assistive Listening Systems[-END TRANSLATE-]</h5>
<p class="standards">[-BEGIN TRANSLATE-]Assistive listening systems shall be identified by the International Symbol of Access for Hearing Loss complying with Figure 703.7.2.4.[-END TRANSLATE-]</p>
